  Red Hat Enterprise Linux Server (v. 6),
  Red Hat Enterprise Linux Server (v. 7),
  Red Hat Enterprise Linux Workstation (v. 6)");
  script_tag(name:"solution", value:"Please Install the Updated Packages.");
